{"tid":511993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[機頂盒案]  三IT人重判21至27個月","createTime":"2017-12-28T04:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T04:21:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"28ba2b505e691cc1e822baddf9393d47c8f9938f","tid":511993,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"海關3年前世界盃舉行期間，搗破一個利用一款電視機頂盒「麥格盒子」非法轉播收費頻道的侵權集團，揭發不法分子利誘在港一名技術員及招攬他人，向一間電視台申請11個收費頻道帳戶，透過獲發的電視台解碼器，全天候把已解密的信號傳送到內地一伺服器，從而令「麥格盒子」可從該伺服器上取得信號，供用家非法收看有關頻道。技術員、其友人及售賣該電視機頂盒的檔主等3人，早前承認串謀詐騙和違反《版權條例》，今(28日)在區院分別被判囚21至27個月。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告依次為<span style=\"color: red;\">技術員</span>鍾羽翔(39歲)、技術員何國祥(53歲)及涉案檔主林兆偉(53歲)。鍾被判囚27個月，而何及林二人則同判囚21個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171228/bkn-20171228122540028-1228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171228%2Fbkn-20171228122540028-1228_00822_001.html&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2FWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b0a11d01\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171228/bkn-20171228122540028-1228_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e1fd3073a0613e4090756ab97f941463ccdaaadf","tid":511993,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>HK No IT</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e7b205358a94bc180d4d5104f65e6141da14c8cc","tid":511993,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"強姦非禮衰11都無判得咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac8173f5b27db130d714fbc44ec8d9bd88cd85d","tid":511993,"uid":14766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7b205358a94bc180d4d5104f65e6141da14c8cc","tid":511993,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"強姦非禮衰11都無判得咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04